International Delphi consensus guidelines for follow-up after prophylactic total 
gastrectomy: the Life after Prophylactic Total Gastrectomy (LAP-TG) study.

Roberts G(1)(2), Benusiglio PR(3), Bisseling T(4), Coit D(5), Davis JL(6), 
Grimes S(7), Guise TA(8), Hardwick R(7), Harris K(9), Mansfield PF(8), Rossaak 
