The Exocrine Pancreas in Cystic Fibrosis in the Era of CFTR Modulation: A Mini 
Review.

McKay IR(1), Ooi CY(2)(3).

Author information:
(1)Wagga Wagga Base Hospital, Wagga Wagga, NSW, Australia.
(2)School of Clinical Medicine, Discipline of Paediatrics and Child Health, 
